   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-1-" mid="271" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="235"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>I wonder if Shalica's plan will work.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-a" mid="272" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="236"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What a relief! Then does it also show the exact location of the relic you are looking for?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-b" mid="273" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="237"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>Woah, relax. I'll read you what is written inside the diary.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-c" mid="274" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="238"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>"Hundreds of years ago, Chiron Island used to be an independent republic free from Childs' rule. At this time, Chiron Island was completely isolated from the outside world, surrounded by a powerful magic force field barrier that not even Childs could break through."</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-d" mid="275" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="239"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>"How this barrier worked remains a mystery, but it is said that the tower at the center could recognize those who might pose a threat to the island and denied their entry. This force field is thought to have protected Chiron Island for about two hundred years since it was first activated."</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-e" mid="276" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="240"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>"For unknown reasons, the great tower started to lose its power and Chiron Island eventually fell under a Child Lord. Without the protection of the barrier, the residents of the island had no choice but to succumb to the Child Lord and their state lost its independence. With this...."</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-f" mid="277" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="241"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>A great tower…! So the relic was a tower!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-g" mid="278" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="242"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>Yes, it must be a tower decorated with gemstones since another legend tells of a statue made of gemstone. Wait, there's more.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-h" mid="279" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="243"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>"What happened to the tower that gave birth to so many legendary tales? According to testimonies from the residents and historical records, the tower eventually broke down into pieces. It is unknown where the debris can be found, but my guess is that it is under the giant tree at the center of the island."</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-i" mid="280" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="244"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>"The enormous tree still boasts its gigantic branches. No one knows exactly when the tree appeared at the center of the island. However, what is certain is that it started to grow after the collapse of the great tower."</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-j" mid="281" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="245"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>"The tree suddenly shot up to reach enormous height as if it was grown by magic. Lord of Chiron Island who regarded it as inauspicious tried to chop it down but the tree was as hard as steel."</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-k" mid="282" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="246"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>"Lord of the island and the villagers tried to cut the tree down for several years but its roots dug deep underground and spread across the center of the island. After learning about this, I made a hypothesis."</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-l" mid="283" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="247"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>"Maybe it's the collapsed tower that magically grew the enormous tree to protect its pieces. If my hypothesis is correct, it would answer many questions."</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-m" mid="284" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="248"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Then…… The tower is at the center of Chiron Island, buried somewhere under a gigantic tree?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-1-n" mid="285" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="249"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>Yes. The center of Chiron Island is tightly guarded with Hirendel's magic.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-1-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-2" mid="286" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="250"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>…….That's bad. I don't know if Hirendel is protecting Chiron Island because he knows about this, but there's no way you can enter the center of the island for now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2351_salica-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2351_salica-2-" mid="287" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="251"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka ponders deeply. Shalica turns to Vernicka.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-a" mid="288" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="252"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>I heard rumours that Hirendel's favourite garden can be found at the center of Chiron Island. Although I'm not sure if the gigantic tree is part of that garden, all I know is that there's no way you can go there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-b" mid="289" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="253"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>I tried getting to the center several times myself but I couldn't break through Hirendel's force field every single time. But... since I know the exact location now, we should find a way to get there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-c" mid="290" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="254"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>We don't know how long that would take, Shalica. Don't you think it's time to find another way?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-d" mid="291" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="255"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Vernicka is right. I just came back from the seabed cave and……. </FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Tell them about the conversation between Hirendel and Casmina that you overheard.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-e" mid="292" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="256"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Hirendel said he's planning to make Merca his garden. Besides, the other Child, Casmina, said she has scary monsters under her. We need to do something fast.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-f" mid="293" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="257"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka sighs.)</FONT> Hirendel has made up his mind to invade Merca. The agents I sent to other Childs are not even back yet…….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-g" mid="294" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="258"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>Vernicka, you know Hirendel doesn't have an army. Even though he's a High Child, wiping Merca out on his own would cause an alarm for the other Childs. Besides, based on what <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT> heard, Hirendel seems reluctant about using Casmina's monsters.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_Salica.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-h" mid="295" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="259"><![CDATA[<html>$Shalica$<BR>Maybe Hirendel wants Merca all for himself or he's a terrible perfectionist who is devising a plan to invade Merca on his own.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-i" mid="296" select_type="4" />
      <talk_question mid="260"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Completed$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2367_vernicka-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2367_vernicka-2-!next" mid="297" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="261"><![CDATA[<html>$Vernicka$<BR>I know he won't attack Merca overnight, but…….</html>]]></talk_question>
